OL,6,Fwill no longer require its crew to
OL,7,Fwork for up to four months without a
OL,8,Fday off - a practice which has been .
OL,10,FThe company has decided to change its
OL,11,Frosters to comply with new rules,
OL,12,Fwhich were enacted in France last
OL,13,Fmonth to improve working conditions
OL,14,Ffor seafarers.
