OL,6,FThe letter says "the new regulation
OL,7,Fcomes into force in June 2024" and
OL,8,Fthat there would be "serious
OL,9,Fconsequences" for violation.
OL,11,FTwo years ago, P&O caused outrage on
OL,12,Fboth sides of the Channel by sacking
OL,13,F786 crew and replacing them with
OL,14,Fagency workers.
OL,16,FLast month, ITV News and the Guardian
OL,17,Freported that P&O was - even lower
OL,18,Fthan the #5.15 an hour P&O told a
OL,19,Fparliamentary select committee .
