OL,3,CP&O tells crew it will comply with
OL,4,CFrench law and reduce their hours
OL,6,FThe new law also compels ferry
OL,7,Foperators between the UK and France to
OL,8,Fpay their crew at least the French
OL,9,Fminimum wage of #9.96 an hour.
OL,11,FThe letter, which was sent by Philcrew
OL,12,F- the agency which supplies workers to
OL,13,FP&O - does not reveal if rates of pay
OL,14,Fwill also change in June.
OL,16,FP&O has signed a voluntary commitment
OL,17,Fto pay seafarers at least the minimum
OL,18,Fwage at some point in the future.
