OL,6,FLouise Haigh MP said: "P&O Ferries
OL,7,Fhave refused to do the right thing
OL,8,Ffrom the beginning of this scandal,
OL,9,Fand they've only been dragged (to this
OL,10,Fpoint) under the threat of criminal
OL,11,Fsanctions and hefty fines by the
OL,12,FFrench government."
OL,14,FP&O Ferries declined to comment or
OL,15,Fanswer questions about the changes it
OL,16,Fhas planned. The company has stated
OL,17,Fpreviously that it always complies
OL,18,Fwith national and international laws
OL,19,Fand that its crews are well-rested.
