OL,3,CP&O tells crew it will comply with
OL,4,CFrench law and reduce their hours
OL,6,FUntil now, P&O has exploited a legal
OL,7,Floophole which exempts the payment of
OL,8,Fthe national minimum wage to seafarers
OL,9,Fwho are employed by an overseas agency
OL,10,Fand work on foreign-registered ships
OL,11,Fin international waters.
OL,13,FIn the UK, legislation to remove this
OL,14,Fexemption is expected to take effect
OL,15,Fin the summer.
