OL,7,Fhas not adopted P&O's low-cost
OL,8,Fbusiness model, shows that any ferries
OL,9,Fcompany which fails to comply with the
OL,10,Fnew law on both sides of the Channel
OL,11,Ffaces a fine of #76,000 a day.
OL,13,FThe boss of P&O has been examining
OL,14,Fworking conditions in Britain.
OL,16,FPeter Hebblethwaite is expected to be
OL,17,Fquestioned by the business and trade
OL,18,Fcommittee on Tuesday May 7.
